namedPeople.description: Chetan Pratap Singh Chauhan (born 21 July 1947) is a former cricketer who played 40 Test matches for India. He played Ranji Trophy for Maharashtra and Delhi. He played most of his international cricket in the late 1970s and was the regular opening partner of Sunil Gavaskar during that period. Chetan Chauhan was appointed as Chairman of NIFT (National Institute of Fashion Technology) from June 2016 to June 2017. He was also twice elected as a Member of Parliament, elected to the Lok Sabha from Amroha in Uttar Pradesh. As of August 2018, he is minister for youth and sports in the state of Uttar Pradesh, India.

transcript.text: Hello and welcome to on Print Shop.
In this video, we'll see how to set the Hire a Designer option.

We will see the significance of Hire a designer, how to enable the Hire a Designer option from the admin panel and how to set the additional options for Hire a Designer which we require from the customer and how to set up the charges for hire a designer option apart from the normal product.
So let's get started.
The importance of creating the hire a designer is that suppose your customer doesn't want any templates that you have opted or he wants you to hire a designer for his product.
So in that case, you need to have higher a designer option.
So let us create a higher a designer option for a yard sign.
So in that situation, you have to go to action add it for any of the product.
And here is an option from product type that is called higher a designer.
You have to enable this option and after that, this option will be displayed on the price calculator in the front store.
So I have enabled this option and let me open this product on the front store.
Now here you will see there is an option called hire designer.
The default will be no.
You can select yes.
Now, right now the pricing of the product is 10.
As soon as I select yes, the pricing will be change.
The pricing becomes 60.
So that means $50.00 I have set as designing price.
Now again one more thing, if you select no and you see there is an option called get started.
But as soon as I select yes in the hire designer, the option would become higher.
As for a designing, OK, now how to set the pricing for the designing for a particular product?
Let us go in here on the product side.
On the setting side, you have an option called pricing.
From pricing you have to set the designing cost for this particular product only right?
So the designing cost is set per product based on the product.
So here I have set as 50.
You can set the way you want and click on save.
So the designing cost is set from settings for the particular product.
Now if the customer on the front stores selects yes, that means he wants you to design for his product.
So he has to select yes from here.
And now here you will see the designing option is there, but there is no information.
So let us go and set some additional options.
Let us assume that you want the name of the company and that is a text box.
This one you have to enable this option.
So this option, this additional option would be displayed only on the hire designer tab.
Now click on save and back.

The other option that you can enable is that for suppose if the customer is having his file that he wants to have his logo or image that he wants to wants you to use so he will send that and for that you have to select this option to allow the customer to upload his own logo or file.
And please don't forget to click this option right and click on save and back.
Additional information can be gained from the customer.
That means additional info mention and you can use that for a text area so more text can be added over here.
And again, do not forget to click on this option.
These three additional options will be displayed on the higher designer options.
Only click on Save and back.
Now we have created 3 fields for designing.
And here from here you can identify that this additional option is only for Hire a designer.
These three fields are for Hire a designer options only.
So now let me go on to the front store.
And right now there are no additional options.
But as soon as I refresh, I'll see three options, 1-2 and three.
So this will be there only if the customer has selected yes.
Now let us go ahead and try to place an order and as when the customer goes and place the order, he will see this kind of information that means logo file and hire a designer.
The cost of hire a designer is also displayed over here on his order details.
So this way you can set the hire a designer options for any of your product.
